I hadn't visited a dentist before and decided to visit Dr. Ashitesh Kumar for Teeth Whitening and Tooth Air Polishing on the recommendation of a friend. Naturally, I cannot benchmark him against another dentist experience, but the following is why I'd love to come back to Dr. Ashitesh Kumar for any dental requirements, and recommend him to others:

1. I showed up at the exact time of my appointment and was pleased to find the Doctor and his Assistant already prepared for the slot. There was no waiting time at all, and the punctuality followed was impressive.

2. Since I had never visited a dentist, I was slightly nervous and had many doubts pertaining to the procedure that'll be followed. Without me asking, Dr. Ashitesh explained me the entire procedure and had me relaxed

3. He kept appraising me on the progress of the procedure and also showed me the progress using a microscopic camera at vital points. This, coupled with his humor/wit had me completely relaxed!

4. The kind of professionalism and warmth with which I was treated was way beyond my expectations. Especially for the price point at which I was offered the above-mentioned treatments!

survey_response.review_text: Coming to this dental clinic has made me trust online ratings, all the more! And, both Dr. Ashitesh and Dr. Meghana made it so easy, efficient, comfortable and clinical! They know their job; they are keen, minute observers; they are super sensitive to the patient's needs; and they are energetic and agile! They also have a very professional nursing team and front desk - note that I've visited them during the pandemic and their safety precautions are precise (read: I say this as a doctor myself!). Finally, my recent visits were time sensitive - I'm shifting to another city, and I was sceptical of completing all the necessary procedures before the end of the month. But, given their sharpness, efficiency and a well planned treatment, Dr. Ashitesh and Dr. Meghana made it possible and perfect! I would recommend them to everyone. Look no further :)
